                 In recurring mode (format 1): week wday month hh:mm
                 In recurring mode (format 2): RJul n hh:mm
                 In date mode:      month day year hh:mm
                 week:  0-6  (0=First, 6=Last)
                 wday:  1-7  (Sunday-Saturday)
                 month: 1-12 (January-December)
                 day:   1-31
                 year:  0-99 (2000-2099)
                 hh:    0-23 (hours)
