                     unknown     - requests were not sent yet.
                     inProcess   - replies were not received yet.
                     up          - server sent SNTP packets.
                     down        - server stopped sending SNTP packets."
        DEFVAL      { unknown }
        ::= { rlSntpServerInetEntry 6 }

